trans-unit.source: This class is internally created and used by the page parser when parsing a `<mobile:ObjectList>` element.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe é criada e usada pelo analisador de página durante a análise de internamente um `<mobile:ObjectList>` elemento.

trans-unit.source: The ObjectListControlBuilder class recognizes statically declared `<Field>` elements and statically declared `<Command>` elements.
trans-unit.target: A classe ObjectListControlBuilder reconhece declarada estaticamente `<Field>` elementos e declarada estaticamente `<Command>` elementos.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectListControlBuilder"></xref> class.
